# Database Lesson Content

## Skills
* A. Create database at Bluehost
    * Create DB
    * Create User
    * List DB
* B. Execute SQL in phpmyadmin
    * CREATE TABLE
    * INSERT
    * SELECT
    * UPDATE
    * DELETE
* C. Connect DB with PHP
    * Connection string
    * Local and Remote connect
* E. List Records
    * Query
    * Render List
    * Render Table
* D. Insert Record
    * SQL INSERT
    * Setting Fields
* F. Functions for Connect, Insert, List
* G. Code library - db.php
* H. Add Record View
* I. List Records View
* J. Edit Record View (Delete)


